<item>
            <title>[LU-16188] Coordinator can put non-started request in STARTED state</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16188</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When the coordinator tries to send multiple HSM actions in&lt;br/&gt;
a single request to agent, if one of the request fails incompat checks in &lt;tt&gt;mdt_hsm_is_action_compat()&lt;/tt&gt;, all the requests are wrongly marked as &lt;tt&gt;STARTED&lt;/tt&gt; but none of the requests are actually sent to the agent. The STARTED requests will never be rescheduled and will fail after timeout.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="72518">LU-16188</key>
